divs: Sighting DetailsHere is a captured UFO from NJ taken a few years ago. Its very similar to the object in the AZ webcam. I have seen another picture somewhere even closer to this object but have yet to locate it. Unknowns don't have to be round in fact they come in many different shapes and sizes including looking like familiar items here on Earth and others are completely different to what we would think. I have many opinions but would rather keep them to myself. I will post that other photo when I find it. Thanks for comparing and looking.
